  <trk>
    <name>Ascent of the Eggerhorn and descent into the Binntal</name>
    <desc>Climb from the valley floor of the young Rhone to the panoramic summit of the Eggerhorn and descend into the original Binntal. The hike impresses with an adventurous discovery of the landscapes and villages of the Binntal Landscape Park.</desc>
    <type>hikingTourTrail</type>
